face_detection_yunet.onnx
=========================

Bundled third-party model, used by the optional face-detection feature
(affectlens.midlevel.load_face_detector via cv2.FaceDetectorYN).

  Model:   YuNet (face_detection_yunet_2023mar)
  Author:  Shiqi Yu and Wei Wu
  Source:  OpenCV Zoo, https://github.com/opencv/opencv_zoo
  License: MIT

YuNet is a light-weight, fast and accurate face detection model. It is
redistributed here under the MIT License; the affectlens code that calls it is
under affectlens's own MIT License. This file exists so the attribution ships
with the model in both the source tree and the built wheel.
